Third_Upgrade_Mod.Creature_Specialist:
{~r}Creature Specialist{~}

												Increases the Attack, Defense and Speed skills of any @Crea1@, @Crea2@ or @Crea3@ for each level attained after @level@th level.

												When in combat @Hero@ further improves @sex@ creatures with:
												Att/Def: {+@attack@}
												Damage: {+@damage@}
												Health: {+@health@%%}
